sentences.english: This article aims to analyze various processing methods for groundwater excavation of the foundation ditch in earthwork construction.
sentences.chinese: 分析土方工程施工中基坑开挖地下水的各种处理办法。

sentences.english: In this paper, the excavation work of deep foundation pit for the north concrete anchor of south branch of Runyang Bridge is introduced.
sentences.chinese: 介绍了润扬大桥南汊北锚碇深基坑工程开挖实例。

sentences.english: Exemplary into about deep foundation pit bracing design methodology.
sentences.chinese: 专题部分为关于深基坑支护设计方法的研究。

sentences.english: In the end, some suggestions for the treatment scheme of confined water for the deep foundation pit were presented.
sentences.chinese: 最后，对基坑承压水的处理提出了一些建议。

sentences.english: The accumulative total displacements at the measuring points on the base top and pile top are somewhat high.
sentences.chinese: 基坑西侧支护体系的基顶和桩顶测点累计位移偏大。

sentences.english: The paper has adopted object function method and created optimization model of foundation ditch precipitation well cluster.
sentences.chinese: 采用目标函数法，建立基坑降水井群优化模型。

sentences.english: Bore-hole cast-in-place pile was filled outside the foundation pit.
sentences.chinese: 对于基坑外的部分，采用钻孔灌注桩补桩。

sentences.english: With the development of city construction, there are more and more deep foundation pit projects.
sentences.chinese: 随着城市建设的发展，深基坑工程增多。

sentences.english: So it becomes more important to study foundation ditch support in deep foundation pit projects.
sentences.chinese: 因此深基坑支护的研究越来越重要。

sentences.english: The South Anchor of Runyang bridge is a super-deep foundation pit.
sentences.chinese: 润扬大桥南锚工程为一大型深基坑工程。

sentences.english: Diaphragm wall is widely used as soil retaining structure in deep excavation in Shanghai.
sentences.chinese: 地下连续墙是上海地区深基坑的主要围护形式。

sentences.english: The paper states the design of the trestle protection of foundation pit of intercepting trunk in Longhugou regulation in Santou City.
sentences.chinese: 阐述汕头市龙湖沟整治中截污干管的基坑支护设计。

sentences.english: Prior to foundation pit excavation, the culvert section shall be prefabricated and carried to position.
sentences.chinese: 基坑开挖前涵节预制并按序运至工点摆放。

sentences.english: "New two pipe method"is a new way to stop the water in deep foundation pit.
sentences.chinese: “新二管法”是一种新型的深基坑止水方法。

sentences.english: In order to construct conveniciently, the wells group was often used to reduce the underground water level.
sentences.chinese: 工程中常采用井群来降低基坑的地下水位，以便施工。

sentences.english: Therefore, the influence of unsteady seepage should be taken into account in the design of retaining wall.
sentences.chinese: 因此，在基坑支护设计中应该考虑非稳定渗流的影响。
